OL,3,CFamily man killed in crash 'sacrificed
OL,4,Chis life to save the woman he loved'
OL,6,FA man who died when a lorry crossed a
OL,7,Fmotorway and collided with six
OL,8,Fvehicles 'sacrificed' his life to save
OL,9,Fhis wife, his family have said.
OL,11,FDavid Lalgee, 64, selflessly turned
OL,12,Fhis car into the path of the lorry to
OL,13,Ftake the impact of the collision,
OL,14,Fensuring his wife Jo, was able to
OL,15,Fescape with her life.
OL,17,FThe grandfather suffered serious
OL,18,Finjuries in the incident at Junction
OL,19,F15 of the M60 near Swinton, in
OL,20,FSalford, on 20 March, and later died
OL,21,Fin hospital.
