OL,3,CFamily man killed in crash 'sacrificed
OL,4,Chis life to save the woman he loved'
OL,6,FHis family have now paid tribute to
OL,7,Fthe "devoted father and proud
OL,8,Fgrandfather" who, they say, was "a
OL,9,Fpillar of love and support to so many".
OL,11,F"He adored his family, and the way he
OL,12,Floved his wife was something truly
OL,13,Fspecial filling their home with
OL,14,Fwarmth, kindness, and steadfast
OL,15,Fdevotion," the family said.
OL,17,F"His absence leaves a void that words
OL,18,Fcannot express.
OL,26,@sD@AOUyD@AOU
