OL,3,CFamily man killed in crash 'sacrificed
OL,4,Chis life to save the woman he loved'
OL,6,F"In his final moments, David did what
OL,7,Fhe had always done - he put others
OL,8,Fbefore himself. With incredible
OL,9,Fbravery, he protected his wife, Jo,
OL,10,Fplacing himself between her and the
OL,11,Foncoming lorry that had crossed the
OL,12,Fcentral reservation.
OL,14,F"He took the full impact, sacrificing
OL,15,Fhis life to save the woman he loved.
OL,17,F"No words can truly capture the man
OL,18,FDavid was."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@AOU
