OL,3,CFamily man killed in crash 'sacrificed
OL,4,Chis life to save the woman he loved'
OL,6,FThey continued: "He was a protector, a
OL,7,Fcarer, the Pastor of Church Alive in
OL,8,FBlackpool, as well as above all else,
OL,9,Fa pillar of love and support to so
OL,10,Fmany.
OL,12,F"He lived to serve others, always
OL,13,Foffering kindness, wisdom, and
OL,14,Funwavering faith.
OL,16,F"David cared for people his whole
OL,17,Flife, not just for own family and
OL,18,Ffriends but he was a proprietor for
OL,19,Fhis own care home for over 30 years,
OL,20,FStockdove care home in Cleveleys where
OL,21,Fhe cared for the elderly.
OL,26,@nD@QOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
