OL,3,CFamily man killed in crash 'sacrificed
OL,4,Chis life to save the woman he loved'
OL,6,F"We cannot imagine anyone ever
OL,7,Fspeaking a bad word about him.
OL,9,F"His selflessness and compassion
OL,10,Ftouched so many lives, and while our
OL,11,Ftime with him was far too short, we
OL,12,Fwill forever cherish the moments and
OL,13,Fmemories he gave us."
OL,15,FDavid was a father to Josh, Tamar, and
OL,16,FBen, as well as a stepfather to Jake,
OL,17,FWill, and Connie, and a grandfather to
OL,18,Fnine grandchildren.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOU
